8 Trademarks

    This Licence does not grant You any right to use any trade names,
    trademarks, service marks, or product names of the Licensor, except as
    required for reasonable and customary use in describing the origin of
    the Covered Source and reproducing the content of the Notice file.

9 Termination

9.1 Any breach of this Licence will automatically terminate Your rights
    under it upon notice of termination from the Licensor. Any third party
    who has received rights under this Licence from You will not have their
    licences terminated provided their licences remain in full compliance
    with this Licence. Sections 1, 6, 7, 8, 9 and 10 will survive any
    termination of this Licence.

9.2 If You are notified of any breach by You of this Licence and You cure
    that breach within 30 days of the notification, your licences will
    continue in full force and effect.

10 General

10.1 If any provision of this Licence is or becomes illegal, invalid or
